replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:11:35.000Z","msg":"呢啲公司唔值得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"老老實實, 寫個test case仲煩過/晒時間過寫個code本身, 正常人/公司都唔會做啦, e.g.<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/b0jZSx/test_case_for_greeting.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fb0jZSx%2Ftest_case_for_greeting.jpg&h=47108e95&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 近十年都未做過唔寫Test Cases既公司<br />\n當件Product有十件八件Components<br />\n啲Test Cases就用嚟救命㗎嘞"},{"pid":"010fc42a6d4a463e39a448636cd03f6043f39847","tid":594292,"uid":167032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T01:27:50.000Z","msg":"rest params<br />\n<br />\na={b:1, c:2}<br />\n...a"},{"pid":"38f88d27f2ec9f3ff451a362b1e91e924c7b1418","tid":594292,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T01:28:38.000Z","msg":"除左react component 有無人會用佢嘅 class object"},{"pid":"77759cb024bd6275eeb19121cdfef8a910b6cc7b","tid":594292,"uid":33883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"以前個Promise(a modernized async function to replace callback)幾好用, e.g.<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/fyN19c/Normal_Function_To_Async_Function_And_Callback_To_Promise.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FfyN19c%2FNormal_Function_To_Async_Function_And_Callback_To_Promise.jpg&h=a14d7755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過Promise已fade out, 而家都轉晒用Async/Await了! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a5b4aefef08dd045772b3eb27204d76f6b32fe","tid":594292,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38f88d27f2ec9f3ff451a362b1e91e924c7b1418","tid":594292,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T01:28:38.000Z","msg":"除左react component 有無人會用佢嘅 class object"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:59:07.000Z","msg":"其實除咗寫React component之外，好多時都會自己Define啲Class出嚟<br />\n我自己多數用嚟寫Strategy<br />\n<br />\nclass Helper {<br />\n  constructor (task) { }<br />\n  doSomething () { }<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\nclass HelperA extends Helper {<br />\n  constructor (...args) { super(...args); }<br />\n  doSomething () { }<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\nclass HelperB extends Helper {<br />\n  constructor (...args) { super(...args); }<br />\n  doSomething () { }<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\nconst helperFactory = (task) =&gt; {<br />\n  if (task === 'A') return new HelperA(task);<br />\n  if (task === 'B') return new HelperB(task);<br />\n  return new Helper(task);<br />\n};<br />\n<br />\nconst helper = helperFactory(task);<br />\nhelper.doSomething();<br />\n<br />\n自從有咗Class之後就唔洗再寫過啲咁嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nfunction Helper () { }<br />\n<br />\nfunction HelperA () { }<br />\n<br />\nHelperA.prototype = Object.create(Helper.prototype);"},{"pid":"0e0d93b7094aab66d4cca98cb2f7adfeeb55e300","tid":594292,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77759cb024bd6275eeb19121cdfef8a910b6cc7b","tid":594292,"uid":33883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"以前個Promise(a modernized async function to replace callback)幾好用, e.g.<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/fyN19c/Normal_Function_To_Async_Function_And_Callback_To_Promise.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FfyN19c%2FNormal_Function_To_Async_Function_And_Callback_To_Promise.jpg&h=a14d7755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過Promise已fade out, 而家都轉晒用Async/Await了! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T10:02:21.000Z","msg":"初初接觸async/await嗰陣成日用<br />\n後嚟都係改用返.then()<br />\n<br />\n個人喜好<br />\n我自己唔係好鍾意用try catch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fc7bbe03a9c9c4a968e6238ad4f7ee9e5447c7","tid":594292,"uid":108937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77759cb024bd6275eeb19121cdfef8a910b6cc7b","tid":594292,"uid":33883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"以前個Promise(a modernized async function to replace callback)幾好用, e.g.<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/fyN19c/Normal_Function_To_Async_Function_And_Callback_To_Promise.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FfyN19c%2FNormal_Function_To_Async_Function_And_Callback_To_Promise.jpg&h=a14d7755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過Promise已fade out, 而家都轉晒用Async/Await了! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"async await 正咁多<br />\n你而家可以用 for loop 去順序async calls<br />\n以前一定要用recursion"}]}